<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Smart Shop Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #2563eb;
            /* Matches your frontend blue-600 */
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .otp-container {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 2px solid #dbeafe;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 10px;
            color: #1e40af;
        }

        .warning {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666666;
            border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f4f4f4;
            color: #999999;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Smart Shop</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Password Reset Request</h2>
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your <strong>Smart Shop</strong> account. Use the code
                below to proceed with the reset process:</p>

            <div class="otp-container">
                <span class="otp-code">
                    <%= otp %>
                </span>
            </div>

            <p>This recovery code is valid for <strong>5 minutes</strong>. For your security, never share this code with
                anyone.</p>

            <div class="warning">
                <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain
                    unchanged.</p>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Best regards,<br><strong>The Smart Shop Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 Smart Shop. All rights reserved.<br>
            This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>